  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BiogasControl
    Main user interface to simulate predefined structures.
    Contains the JTabbedPane implementing the panels in vrl.biogas.biogascontrol.panels
    BiogasControlClass
    Parent class for the main panels BiogasControl/BiogasUserControl
    BiogasControlPluginConfigurator
    Plugin Configurator to export Eclipse project into VRL plugin
    Select "Export as runnable JAR" - Check "Package required libraries into generated JAR"
    BiogasUserControl
    Main user interface to simulate user defined structures.
    Contains the JTabbedPane implementing the panels in vrl.biogas.biogascontrol.panels.
    To be used in combination with the Iterator class.
    Iterator
    Simulation iterator to be used with the BiogasUserControl.
    Used to starts the simulation.
    MainPanelContainerType
    Type representation in VRL for the main panels BiogasControl/BiogasUserControl.
